.SS GET_FIELD_SIZES
.PP
.proto_get_field_sizes
.PP
Returns an array whose elements contain the length of the longest
string for each field in the table.
Use these numbers to inform formatting of the table on a printout.
.RS 4
.arg_handle
.arg_return_array
.RE
.PP
